      "writtenOn": "2018-09-28T14:52:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, I had the same thought.  I don\u0027t think I\u0027d be confused by any of\n\n   - .Run(\"which\", \"go\")\n   - .RunCwd(\"which\", \"go\")\n   - .RunWithCwd(\".\", \"which\", \"go\")\n   - .RunIn(\".\", \"which\", \"go\")\n   - .Cwd(\".\").Run(\"which\", \"go\")\n\nwhich I\u0027d all expect to do the same thing.",
      "parentUuid": "81841911_d721361a",
